ZH: 当你梳头发的时候，头发之间会产生静电。
EN: When you brush your hair, static electricity is generated between the hair strands.

ZH: 冬天干燥的天气容易引发静电。
EN: Dry weather in winter easily triggers static electricity.

ZH: 女孩子在穿裙子的时候要防止静电。
EN: Girls should be cautious of static electricity when wearing skirts.

ZH: 静电可能导致电子设备的故障。
EN: Static electricity can cause malfunctions in electronic devices.

ZH: 使用带防静电功能的清洁布可以避免静电。
EN: Using an anti-static cleaning cloth can help prevent static electricity.

ZH: 待在空调房间里容易积聚静电。
EN: Staying in an air-conditioned room can easily accumulate static electricity.

ZH: 静电可以使相同的物体互相吸引。
EN: Static electricity can make identical objects attract each other.

ZH: 不小心触碰金属物体会感受到静电。
EN: Accidentally touching a metal object can make you feel a static electricity shock.

ZH: 看到闪电时，那是静电的放电现象。
EN: When you see lightning, it is the discharge of static electricity.

