EN: Wearing synthetic fiber clothing easily leads to static electricity buildup.

ZH: 裸露的木地板容易产生静电。
EN: Exposed wooden floors are prone to static electricity generation.

ZH: 将手搓热后再触碰金属可以消除静电。
EN: Rubbing your hands together before touching metal can neutralize static electricity.

ZH: 用湿布擦拭电子屏幕可减少静电的积聚。
EN: Wiping electronic screens with a damp cloth can reduce static electricity buildup.

ZH: 持续的静电对皮肤有害。
EN: Prolonged exposure to static electricity is harmful to the skin.

ZH: 移动的物体在摩擦时会产生静电。
EN: Moving objects generate static electricity during friction.

